            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "2618": {
          "vnum": 2618,
          "name": "The High Grasses",
          "description": "Tall grass surrounds you and press in on you. You would never find your way back if you strayed from the trail you follow. You arrive at an intersection in the trail, with paths leading north, east, and south.",
          "grid_x": -3,
          "grid_y": -2,
          "exits": {
            "n": {
              "to_vnum": 2619,
              "to_zone": "The Hills North of Mareldja",
              "to_room_name": "The Edge of the River Telemacus",
              "direction": "n",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "2619": {
          "vnum": 2619,
          "name": "The Edge of the River Telemacus",
          "description": "A narrow but fast river flows here, and you recall from your childhood the legend of Telemacus and his fate at the hands of the mountain dwarves. For a second, you imagine that the river runs red with his blood--it must have been your imagination, but you nevertheless feel uneasy. The river is strangely silent as it works its way eastward toward Lake Arlyn.",
          "grid_x": -3,
          "grid_y": -3,
          "exits": {
            "w": {
              "to_vnum": 2620,
              "to_zone": "The Hills North of Mareldja",
              "to_room_name": "A Mysterious Blessing",
              "direction": "w",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "2620": {
          "vnum": 2620,
          "name": "A Mysterious Blessing",
          "description": "How strange! You have chanced upon an old bridge spanning the River Telemacus. Although the wood is clearly ages old, it still seems firm and stable.",
          "grid_x": -4,
          "grid_y": -3,
          "exits": {
            "n": {
              "to_vnum": 2621,
              "to_zone": "The Hills North of Mareldja",
              "to_room_name": "A Landing on the North Side of the River Telemacus",
              "direction": "n",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "2621": {
          "vnum": 2621,
          "name": "A Landing on the North Side of the River Telemacus",
          "description": "You stand on a wide stone ledge from which you can see far to the east across the dead hills. To the west, a narrow and treacherous path leads toward a waterfall high in the mountains. A bridge leads south across the river.",
          "grid_x": -4,
          "grid_y": -4,
          "exits": {
            "e": {
              "to_vnum": 3089,
              "to_zone": "The Hills North of Mareldja",
