        "220": {
          "vnum": 220,
          "name": "The Western Meadow",
          "description": "You stand at one end of a long meadow split by a wide river. To the north you see the source of the river as the water crashes down aglow with the light of the sun. The scents of green grass and flowers fill your nostrils as you stroll through the meadow. The meadow continues eastward. (You are riding atop a riding bird.)",
