        "221": {
          "vnum": 221,
          "name": "Meadow Middle",
          "description": "Ah! There's nothing as scenic and heart warming as the middle of a meadow. You feel almost blessed as you wander about, savoring the delicate sweetness dancing with your every sense. The glimmer of a waterfall catches your eye and you watch the water falling in its eternal path for quite some time. The meadow continues east and west, and hills lie to the north. (You are riding atop a riding bird.)",
