        "222": {
          "vnum": 222,
          "name": "The Meadow by the River",
          "description": "The river separates the meadow from the more wooded lands in the northern valley. The woods seem almost enchanted, and above the forest you see a shimmering green haze. Looking northwest, tracing the river as it winds through the hills, you spot a waterfall, and a full circle rainbow. (You are riding atop a riding bird.)",
