        "223": {
          "vnum": 223,
          "name": "The Forest of Evermore",
          "description": "While the enchantment of the forest seems to light your way, it is most certainly not an open welcome. Certain paths are easy to follow, while others are practically impossible to even spot. The most unwelcome direction, it seems, is north. (You are riding atop a riding bird.)",
