        "224": {
          "vnum": 224,
          "name": "The Temple of Isvaelin",
          "description": "Hidden within this silent section of the forest, a low dome of grey stone rises from beneath a carpet of needles. Brilliant light from within the dome illuminates a flight of marble steps that descend into the southern section, and a melodious chant in an odd tongue resonates amongst the trees. The smooth polish of the stone and the lack of the otherwise ever-present needles upon its surface attest to the reverence of the temple's worshipers. (You are riding atop a riding bird.)",
          "grid_x": 1,
          "grid_y": -3,
