              "name": "Elven archer",
              "description": "The archer is quite grand in her forest camouflage attire.  She holds her bow at the ready should you take any undesirable action.",
              "unique": true
            }
          ]
        },
        "2547": {
          "vnum": 2547,
          "name": "The River Through the Hills",
          "description": "The nameless river that drains Lake Arlyn flows lazily downward through the hills here. Although the river is fairly deep, it is also slow and would be no problem to cross. Strangely, despite the abundance of water, the hills retain their blackened shade, and you recognize the curse of the mountain dwarves at work.",
          "grid_x": 0,
